{"tid":539124,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視大崩壞 ！今復牌跌停 18萬股民悲慘大逃殺","createTime":"2018-01-24T09:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:44:27.000Z","uid":101945,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac9980be1e7f5599339426c706305cb01af5ba2","tid":539124,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"樂視因爆發財務危機、停牌9個月，今日重新復牌，但一開盤就封死跌停，股價報13.8元人民幣（下同），開盤不到10分鐘，成交量突破1萬手，18萬股民慘烈大逃亡。<br />\n<br />\n截至10點左右，掛在跌停板上的賣單超過726萬手，且還在不斷增加中，對於有投資人竟敢「空中接刀」外界也頗敢意外。<br />\n<br />\n多家基金公司分析師看空樂視後市，並下調公司的估值，將樂視股價從停牌時的15.33元人民幣，下砍至3.90元左右，至少重挫近75%，樂視網恐要再吞13根跌停。<br />\n<br />\n樂視網曾是陸股的重要權值股之一，雖已被深證成指、深證100指數、創業板指3大指數「剔除」，但復牌之後若持續跌停，仍會對當前疲軟的創業板帶來負面效應。<br />\n<br />\n創辦人賈躍亭目前持有樂視網10.24億股，其中10.2億股已質押給金融機構，幾乎全數質押。樂視網復牌後，股價一旦跌破其平倉線，賈躍亭質押股份可能會遭強制平倉，不過因賈躍亭資產遭法院凍結，強制平倉仍要法院點頭。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，樂視陷入財務危機，股價一路慘崩，讓不少股民哀號。《經濟觀察報》報導，2014年底，樂視股民老毛在「高人」指點下以33元買進，期間股價一路飆升，達到最高點近180元，老毛身價在半年內從400萬變成5000萬。但2015年5月中旬開始，樂視股價「跌跌不休」，用融資槓桿讓老毛的5000萬只剩下不到100萬，他感嘆「豪賭樂視3年，如今都是黃粱一夢。」<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)"},{"pid":"742d5efe9d40acd9dde6e3eced8ce9f75f514756","tid":539124,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"邊個會去接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e161a78fcd435d1661ec62a4e466c43b840c8d8e","tid":539124,"uid":28163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"742d5efe9d40acd9dde6e3eced8ce9f75f514756","tid":539124,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"邊個會去接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"自己友<br />\n之後再宣布 搵到金主<br />\n其實係假既 又話唔注<br />\n炒幾轉 之後執凹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6c4946453b0743095692644fc198180fb447dc","tid":539124,"uid":27851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩先簽左兩年now sports <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498e68becf97a7999df5ee202f308e946f1b76c8","tid":539124,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"由180跌到得返10%都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656477658882ae5f157fe01a3e88e6c138992c18","tid":539124,"uid":36354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由180跌到得返10%都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有送過股"},{"pid":"c46cb5f3079b16866c5a8e8d4b5070b13064ceca","tid":539124,"uid":27150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"貪心佬升到5000萬仲唔走"},{"pid":"30f086e7355d035da3fbc1541b62f3faa4d20a1c","tid":539124,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da6c4946453b0743095692644fc198180fb447dc","tid":539124,"uid":27851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩先簽左兩年now sports <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"冇影響啦<br />\n變銀主盤now仲開心"},{"pid":"1ea3dd58c830a6e9a7e4c2bea4868c501101427f","tid":539124,"uid":47776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"等睇海航變樂視2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0eb745b9e46ed759d1f36f4612f638d235ffc18","tid":539124,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}